{"tid":1789062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友煮飯....","createTime":"2019-12-19T07:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T09:46:47.000Z","uid":192319,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"df444cd715ed3ca4d34aab62074173fe0e6184b6","tid":1789062,"uid":192319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:35:57.000Z","msg":"尋晚女朋友話煮飯比我同阿爸食<br />\n一個清水煮菜苗(女朋友話上湯豆苗)<br />\n一個蕃茄薯仔金針菇煮肥牛<br />\n仲有茄子炒茄子(落日本一包包即食個啲魚香茄子醬)<br />\n<br />\n其他都冇乜事<br />\n不過佢個茄子個心係生嘅(脆卜卜)<br />\n反而外面已經燶哂<br />\n<br />\n佢茄子食咗兩舊就冇再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢就叫我食哂佢<br />\n我明知生嘅食到一半真係頂唔順就話飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋晚都冇乜事<br />\n今日起身感覺好唔對路<br />\n胃痛發燒<br />\n周身骨痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家等緊樓下醫生4點開門<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有類似經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n圍下爐<br />\n<br />\nP.S 尋晚以為冇事冇影相"},{"pid":"fe772292dec3142b716ddb3242bd967e942c17ed","tid":1789062,"uid":158273,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:36:30.000Z","msg":"你女朋友都係一番好意<br />\n俾多次機會佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ccf676480318a3bb533ac61405d78d36a9c8bf","tid":1789062,"uid":192319,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fe772292dec3142b716ddb3242bd967e942c17ed","tid":1789062,"uid":158273,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:36:30.000Z","msg":"你女朋友都係一番好意<br />\n俾多次機會佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:37:35.000Z","msg":"我容乜易冇下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a5e9a40528429d8b5d59a0a7e75ed065114f41","tid":1789062,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0